Title: Fix stored XSS in description fields
Class: security
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1629379731
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p10

Users with the permission to add/edit items in the custmize menu (views, topics,
etc.) could trigger stored XSS in the overview page.

FEED-6322
